hopobject.body: I'm a housewife methylprednisolone 4mg side effects weight gain Evan Rachel Wood is perhaps best known for her relationship with goth band hero Marilyn Manson - the weird age difference that shocked parents, the tattoos that made their relationship permanent even though they never walked down the aisle, the gross public displays of affection. Now, back on the market, she tells Esquire something that could explain her love for the long-haired man who wore more makeup than she did: she likes women too.
